How do I register for an account on Car Go?

To start using Car Go, you\'ll need to create an account. Tap on the \'Sign Up\' button found on the home screen. Fill in your full name, email address, phone number, CNIC, and create a secure password. You will receive an OTP on phone number; enter the OTP to verify your phone number. Finally, provide any additional information needed to complete your profile setup. By following these steps, you\'ll be ready to start booking cars with Car Go. If you face any issues during the registration process, don\'t hesitate to contact our support team for help. Welcome to Car Go, and enjoy your ride!
How do I book a car on Car Go?

To book a car on Car Go, start by logging into your account. Browse through the available cars by using the search filters to find the one that suits your needs. Once you have selected a car, click on the \"Contact Renter\" button. Communicate with the renter to discuss your requirements, including pick-up and drop-off dates and locations. After agreeing on the terms, you can finalize the booking with the renter.
How can users upload ads on Car Go?

To upload ads on Car Go, users can initiate the process by converting their personal accounts into company accounts, If you don\'t have company account. Once the account is successfully converted, users gain access to upload Ads by clicking on \"+New Car\" button available in My Ads.
How can I convert my personal account into a company account on Car Go?

If you currently have a user account on Car Go and wish to access advanced features such as uploading ads and managing your rental listings more effectively, converting your account to a company account is a seamless process. Simply navigate to the \"My Ads\" section within the Car Go app. Upon clicking on the \"My Ads\" item, a dialog will prompt you to convert your account into a company account. By filling in your company name, you can swiftly initiate the conversion process. Once completed, your account will be upgraded, with your new company account, you\'ll have the ability to upload ads.
How do I find the nearest car rental options on Car Go?

Finding the nearest car rental options on Car Go is a seamless process designed to help you locate the perfect vehicle for your needs. To begin, simply click on the search button from the home screen to navigate to the search screen. Here, you\'ll find a range of filters and search options to refine your results. To locate the nearest car rental options, you can utilize the location-based search feature. By enabling location services or manually entering your location, Car Go will display a list of rental options closest to you. Once you\'ve identified a listing that interests you, simply click on it to view more details. Here, you\'ll find information about the rental, including photos, pricing, and availability. With Car Go\'s intuitive search functionality, you can easily find and book the nearest car rental options, ensuring a convenient and efficient rental experience.
